Lines.Line: Nothing evens a race like an axe to the kneecaps.
The Gods look after fools, children, and drunkards... humans usually count for two out of three.
Nothing a hammer can’t solve!
Give me a row of necks and room to swing and all weariness will fall from me!
Today is a good day for someone else to die!
You can kill a dwarf, but you can never vanquish one!
